 major talking point of the Games.\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 1036, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif's place\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 961}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's division\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 985}, {\"ngram\": \"a major talking point\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1022}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1035}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of Khelif's former opponents, Amy Broadhurst, has given her take on the issue.\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1071, \"end\": 1085, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amy_Broadhurst\", \"score\": 0.999994937526562, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Amy Broadhurst\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amy_Broadhurst\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amy_Broadhurst\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif's former opponents\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1069}, {\"ngram\": \"her take\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1105}, {\"ngram\": \"the issue\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1118}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Irish fighter defeated Khelif in the gold medal bout at the World Championships two years ago.\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1219, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1125, \"end\": 1130, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9523025225909653, \"rank\": 0.029923412654222006, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1154}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medal\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1172}, {\"ngram\": \"bout\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1177}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championships\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1204}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Posting on X before Thursday's bout, she wrote: \\\"Have a lot of people texting me over Imane Khelif.\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1319, \"entities\": [{\